Four trucks were involved in an accident on the N3 towards Johannesburg near Winterton on Wednesday morning causing major traffic disruptions. Spokesperson for the Road Traffic Inspectorate, Zinhle Mali, has advised motorists to use the R616 while authorities were busy clearing the scene. Meanwhile, there was another truck accident on the N3 towards Pietermaritzburg causing traffic problems. Small vehicles are being diverted to the R102 while trucks are stuck in the traffic jam.